.SH NAME
spi_nor_init_uniform_erase_map \- Initialize uniform erase map
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" spi_nor_init_uniform_erase_map
.BI "(struct spi_nor_erase_map *map "  ","
.BI "u8 erase_mask "  ","
.BI "u64 flash_size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "map" 12
the erase map of the SPI NOR
.IP "erase_mask" 12
bitmask encoding erase types that can erase the entire
flash memory
.IP "flash_size" 12
the spi nor flash memory size
